	* [r11018] src/opt_control/propagation.F90,
	  src/opt_control/target_density_inc.F90, src/td/propagator.F90: A
	  couple of bugs fixed: the propagator_dt routine did not handle
	  well the dt<0
	  case, and one uninitialized variable.

