2014-01-31 13:13  micael

	* [r11696] src/hamiltonian/kick.F90,
	  testsuite/real_time/17-absorption-spin_symmetry.01-gs.inp,
	  testsuite/real_time/17-absorption-spin_symmetry.02-td_spin_and_density_kick.inp,
