2014-09-04 17:03  dstrubbe

	* [r12478] external_libs/spglib-1.5.2/src/hall_symbol.c,
	  external_libs/spglib-1.5.2/src/kpoint.c,
	  external_libs/spglib-1.5.2/src/mathfunc.h,
