	* [r13939] src/states/states_io.F90: Octopus now prints the density
	  of states to the terminal each SCF
	  iteration. These are some examples:
	  
	  ---------------------------------------------%------------------------
	  ----%------------------------------------%-%-%----%-------------------
	  ----%------------------------------------%-%-%----%-------------------
	  ---%%-----------------------------%%%%--%%-%%%--%%%-------------------
	  ---%%-----------------------------%%%%%%%%%%%%--%%%----------------%--
	  --%%%------------------------%---%%%%%%%%%%%%%%-%%%----------------%--
	  %-%%%------------------------%%--%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%--------------%%%--
	  %-%%%---------------%----%---%%%-%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%----------%-%%%%--
	  %%%%%--------------%%%%--%%--%%%-%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%----------%%%%%%%-
	  %%%%%%-------------%%%%--%%%%%%%-%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%----------%%%%%%%-
	  ^
	  
	  
	  
	  -----------------------------------------------%----------------------
	  -----------------------------------------------%----------------------
	  ----------------------------------------------%%----------------------
	  ---------------------------------------%-----%%%----------------------
	  -------------------------------%-%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%---------------------
	  --------------------------%%-%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%---------------------
	  -----------------------%%-%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%--------------------
	  --------------------%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%--------------------
	  ---------------%-%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%-%-%----------------
	  --------------%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%-%%-%-%-----------
	  ^
	  

